OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs call for boy-focused   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsex education strategy     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sex education lessons must engage boys 
OL,6, and young men in order to tackle "a    
OL,7, scourge" of sexual harassment and      
OL,8, violence in schools, according to a    
OL,9, group of MPs.                          
OL,11,FThe inquiry by the Women and Equalities
OL,12,FCommittee heard relationships, sex and 
OL,13,Fhealth education (RSHE) was "less      
OL,14,Fapplicable" to boys than to girls.     
OL,16,FIt is calling for lessons to be made   
OL,17,Fcompulsory in sixth forms and colleges.
OL,19,FThe government says it is developing   
OL,20,Ffurther guidance for schools.          
